<div class="row">
  <div class="col">
    <h3 class="mt-3 mt-md-0">Linguistics after Dark liveshow |  7:00 PM in T√≠r na n√ìg</h3>
    
    
      <i>Featuring Eli Morris-Heft and Sarah Cowett</i><br />
    
    <p>Modern usage got you tense? Can‚Äôt start up your conjugator? Or maybe you‚Äôd just like to make like a schwa and destress. Submit questions to the Linguistics After Dark live show with your burning language questions, and Sarah and Eli will answer them for you. Just one catch: they can‚Äôt do any research before answering. If your language is making a funny noise, they‚Äôll get to the bottom of it, with some rowdy discussion, bad nerdy jokes, and a lot of linguistics along the way</p>

  </div>
